# Student Dashboard Implementation Plan

This document outlines the proposed architecture and components for the Student Dashboard feature.

## User Review Required

The user requested a premium, highly aesthetic design with dynamic animations and modern color palettes. I will implement a sleek, modern UI using Tailwind conventions via standard CSS (or inline styles/CSS files depending on the existing setup). Please review the component structure below.

## Proposed Changes

We will create a specific folder structure to organize the Student Dashboard cleanly.

### `src/components/dashboard/student`
This directory will contain all the relevant files for the Student Dashboard to maintain modularity.

#### [NEW] [StudentDashboard.jsx](file:///d:/Engineering/SE/SEM%204/Mini%20Project/src/components/dashboard/student/StudentDashboard.jsx)
The main container holding the overall layout. It will manage state for active tabs (Attendance, Marks, Assignments) and fetch necessary data using comments.

#### [NEW] [StudentDashboard.css](file:///d:/Engineering/SE/SEM%204/Mini%20Project/src/components/dashboard/student/StudentDashboard.css)
The stylesheet for the dashboard layout, tabs, flags, and highly aesthetic components.

#### [NEW] [TopBar.jsx](file:///d:/Engineering/SE/SEM%204/Mini%20Project/src/components/dashboard/student/TopBar.jsx)
Displays the Website Name (left), Student Flag (center), and Profile Icon/Student ID (right). Clicking the Profile Icon shows a dropdown menu with Profile, Settings, Notifications, and Log out options.

#### [NEW] [AttendanceTab.jsx](file:///d:/Engineering/SE/SEM%204/Mini%20Project/src/components/dashboard/student/AttendanceTab.jsx)
Displays the top-level attendance flag, timetable, and month-by-month grid indicating attendance status (absent, present, mix, off-day).

#### [NEW] [MarksTab.jsx](file:///d:/Engineering/SE/SEM%204/Mini%20Project/src/components/dashboard/student/MarksTab.jsx)
Sub-tabs for IA Marks and Term Work Marks. Displays subject-wise scores and risk flags.

#### [NEW] [AssignmentsTab.jsx](file:///d:/Engineering/SE/SEM%204/Mini%20Project/src/components/dashboard/student/AssignmentsTab.jsx)
Displays a 2x2 grid representing New, Delayed, Pending, and Submitted assignments with their counts and lists. 

